div.bibl: Svenska Tribunen-Nyheter, May 25, 1921. FEDERAL APPOINTMENT FOR KJELIANDER [Half-tone, one column sixth of a page, full-face picture of John Kjellander]

body.p: Our countryman former Alderman and City Sealer John Kjellander, of this city, has been appointed supervising prohibition agent for the district comprising the states of Michigan, Indiana, and Wisconsin. He succeeds Ralph W. Stone.
